This file exists only so //go:embed all:frontend/dist compiles when the real
Svelte bundle hasn't been built (e.g. a 'go install' build, which can't run the
Node toolchain). The real bundle is generated by 'make web-build' and gitignored.

NOTE: it must NOT be a dot-file — Go omits dot-prefixed files from module zips,
which would leave this directory empty and break the embed for 'go install'.
